        "timestamp": "2018-03-23 10:39:45.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nAs an example URLUtilitiesTest.java should contain valid test case for each public method. By valid I mean test checking if what method returned was what we expected. Not just checking not null.\n\nHere is an example test that actually tests something:\n\n\t@Test\n\tpublic void shouldGenerateProperFeedURL() {\n\t\t//given\n\t\tint feedId = 10;\n\n\t\t//when\n\t\tString feedUrl = URLUtilities.generateFeedURL(feedId);\n\n\t\t//then\n\t\tassertThat(feedUrl).isEqualTo(\"https://feeds-drtr.web.att.com/feed/10\");\n\t}",
